snippet: Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger has warned the Premier League not to underestimate the enormous spending power of Chinese football after the Asian country secured another high-profile signing on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger has warned the Premier League not to underestimate the enormous spending power of Chinese football after the Asian country secured another high-profile signing on Friday.

headline.main: Wenger Urges Premier League to Be Wary of Chinese Riches
headline.print_headline: Wenger Urges Premier League to Be Wary of Chinese Riches
